              Stories Applied offers a requirements process that saves time,
              eliminates rework, and leads directly to better software.The best
              way to build software that meets users' needs is to begin with "
              user stories": simple, clear, brief descriptions of functionality
              that will be valuable to real users. In User Stories Applied, Mike
